title: Charlton Bullseye # 1-5
description:
Charton Bullseye was a fanzine published from 1975-76 by the CPL Gang highlighting Charlton Comics. It was a large format publication, with color covers on card stock and black & white interiors. Charton Bullseye published several previously unpublished Charlton superhero and adventure stories, along with articles on Charlton comics, news, reviews, pinups, and more.

Issues 

1. First half of unpublished Captain Atom #90 story, finished by John Byrne
2. Second half of unpublished Captain Atom story
3. Kung Fu Issue, unpublished "Unknown Country" by Sanho Kim intended for Yang.
4. new E-man story and first half of unpublished final Doomsday+1 story.
5. new The Question story by Alex Toth and second half of unpublished final Doomsday+1 story
